      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Yeah generics over primitive types would is a must-have feature. Here is a link to a proposal for it <a href=\"http://openjdk.java.net/jeps/218\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">openjdk.java.net/jeps/218</a>"
